            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Prerequisites</h3>In this text, we explore how the human body served as the basis for numerical systems. For more details, we recommend starting with:</p><p><ul><li><htcite0>: show how we change from our fingers to geometric pictures.</li><li><htcite1>: Illustrating the relationship between our ancestors and numbers.</li><li><htcite2>: Presents the names of generations and numerical orders to the reader.</li></ul></p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "9618a83e-f232-49db-84f6-fc3455a3f1d1",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
                     "page": "Drawing to count",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "07",
                        "day": "25"
                     }
                  },
                  {
