      {
         "id": "SECTION_andes",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Andean numerical systems</h3><h4>Quipus</h4>Quipus operate under the same principles as our decimal system, with the key difference being that instead of adding numbers to the left when writing larger numbers, knots are added above.</p><p class=\"desc\"><img src=\"images/HistoryTracers/Andes_Quipu.png\" class=\"imgcenter\" id=\"imgAndesQuipu\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgAndesQuipu', '0%')\"/><b>Figure 1</b>: Quipu representation. The source code is available in GitHub of the project (<htcite0>).</p><p><h4>The Yuapana</h4>The <i>\"Yupana Inka Tawa Pukllay\"</i> method utilized on this page was developed and published by Dhavit Prem (<htcite1>) of the Yupanki Association (<htcite2>). This method follows the vertical model of <i>Yupana</i>, as presented by Felipe Guaman Poma de Ayala (<htcite3>). When the maximum value, nine (9), is reached, calculations continue in the row above.</p><p>The relationship between <i>Yupana</i> orders and decimal orders is straightforward, as both systems use the same range of numbers:</p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "240800f3-ede4-4deb-9d4e-915a3a03fa68",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
                     "page": "Source-code",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2024",
                        "month": "05",
                        "day": "30"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "2d2ea4a5-506b-4dbf-aaa4-3a10a8fbbd9c",
                     "text": "Prem",
                     "page": "Dhavit",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2018",
                        "month": "07",
                        "day": "25"
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "a62b520a-f443-4d83-ab51-b99c9a46dab8",
                     "text": "Prem, Dhavit",
