            {
               "text": "<p><table id=\"yupana2\" class=\"tawapukllay\"> <tr><th>King (<i>Ajaw</i>)</th><th>Generation</th><th>Order</th><th>Decimal Order</th><th>First number</th><th>Last number</th></tr> <tr><td><i>Yax Pasaj Chan Yopaat</i></td><td>Son</td><td><i>-YOQ/-NIYOQ</i></td><td>Ones</td><td><b>0</b></td><td><b>9</b></td></tr> <tr><td><i>K’ahk’ Yipyaj Chan K’awiil</i></td><td>Father</td><td><i>CHUNKA</i></td><td>Tens</td><td><b>10</b></td><td><b>99</b></td></tr> <tr><td><i>Waxaklajuun Ubaah K’awiil</i></td><td>Grandfather</td><td><i>PACHAQ</i></td><td>Hundreds</td><td><b>100</b></td><td><b>999</b></td></tr> <tr><td><i>K’ahk Uti’ Witz’ K’awiil</i></td><td>1st Great-Grandfather</td><td><i>WARANQA</i></td><td>Thousands</td><td><b>1,000</b></td><td><b>9,999</b></td></tr> <tr><td><i>Butz’ Chan</i></td><td>2nd Great-Grandfather</td><td><i>HUNU</i></td><td>Ten Thousands</td><td><b>10,000</b></td><td><b>99,999</b></td></tr> <tr><td><i>Tzi B’alam</i></td><td>3rd Great-Grandfather</td><td><i>&nbsp;</i></td><td>Hundred Thousands</td><td><b>100,000</b></td><td><b>999,999</b></td></tr> <tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td>4th Great-Grandfather</td><td><i>&nbsp;</td></i><td>Millions</td><td><b>1,000,000</b></td><td><b>9,999,999</b></td></tr> <tr><td><i>Wi’ Yohl K’inich</i></td><td>5th Great-Grandfather</td><td><i>&nbsp;</i></td><td>Ten Millions</td><td><b>10,000,000</b></td><td><b>99,999,999</b></td></tr> <tr><td><i>Bahlam Nehn</i></td><td>6th Great-Grandfather</td><td><i>&nbsp;</i></td><td>Hundred Millions</td><td><b>100,000,000</b></td><td><b>999,999,999</b></td></tr> <tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td>7th Great-Grandfather</td><td><i>&nbsp;</i></td><td>One Billions</td><td><b>1,000,000,000</b></td><td><b>9,999,999,999</b></td></tr> </table></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><b>Table 3</b>: Numerical limits and the family.<br />The names of the kings (<i>ajawob</i>) mentioned in this table are documented by Anastasia Hutnick, Catherine Docter, and Dorie R. Budet (<htcite0> ; <htcite1>).<br />The generational names were sourced from the <i>\"Dicionário de Genealogia\"</i> by Gilber Rubim Rangel (<htcite2> ;<htcite3> ; <htcite4>).</p><p>To visualize a decimal number on the <i>Yupana</i>, you can enter it in the numerical box and click <i class=\"fa-solid fa-play\" style=\"color: Tomato;\" name=\"ignoreme\"></i>:</p>",
