               "text": "<p><h3>Conclusion</h3>In this text, we deepened our understanding of various Indigenous numerical systems, exploring both their differences and their similarities with our modern numerical system. To conclude, we invite you to reflect:</p><p><center><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\">?</div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Reflection 1: Is there a last number?</b><br />We explored various numerical systems used for different types of counting, and in none did we find a rule that prevents the addition of more numbers. Could there be a final number in these systems?</div></div></center></p>",
